00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,060
Sabihin mo sa kanya

513
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:39,780
para mailabas si Xiao Weiran

514
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:41,440
sa lahat ng gastos.

515
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:42,480
Kung kinakailangan,

516
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:45,110
magagamit niya ang marriage alliance
bilang leverage.

517
00:25:45,110 --> 00:25:45,640
Oo.

518
00:25:53,590 --> 00:25:54,590
May pinadala lang si Xia Jingshi

519
00:25:54,590 --> 00:25:55,270
sa Zhengnian Hall

520
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:56,470
para magtanong tungkol kay Ning Fei.

521
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:57,480
Maliban diyan,

522
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,140
wala na siyang ibang ginawa.

523
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,400
Sinong mag-aakalang
Prinsipe ng Zhennan

524
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,660
magiging walang puso?

525
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:03,720
Si Ning Fei ay naging

526
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,110
sa hirap at ginhawa kasama niya.

527
00:26:05,110 --> 00:26:06,510
Ngayong namamatay na si Ning Fei,

528
00:26:06,510 --> 00:26:08,110
nakatalikod lang siya.

529
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,020
Kamahalan,

530
00:26:09,110 --> 00:26:09,880
hindi ba siya natatakot

531
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,210
nakakasira ng loob sa kanyang mga tauhan?

532
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:15,680
Ipinaalam ko sa iyo ang kalagayan ni Ning Fei

533
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:16,700
kay Xia Jingshi

534
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,640
hindi para makita kung gaano siya kalamig

535
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,910
sa kanyang mga nasasakupan.

536
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,080
Saka ano ang balak mo?

537
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,600
Kung isang Jinxiu guard officer

538
00:26:23,610 --> 00:26:25,870
namatay sa Susha bago ang kasal,

539
00:26:26,070 --> 00:26:27,530
anuman ang dahilan,

540
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:29,000
maaari itong sabotahe

541
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:30,330
ang alyansa ng kasal.

542
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:31,920
Xia Jingshi

543
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,200
hindi gumawa ng kaguluhan

544
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:34,560
Tungkol kay Ning Fei

545
00:26:34,720 --> 00:26:37,720
ibig sabihin ay ayaw
din niyang masira ang alyansa.

546
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,050
Kaya iniisip ng Kamahalan

547
00:26:39,350 --> 00:26:41,750
itong marriage alliance ay
bahagi ng kanyang plano?

548
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:42,310
Hindi.

549
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,160
Hindi si Xia Jingshi

550
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,280
