00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:10,550
[Ling Feng, Master ng Zhengnian Villa]

607
00:29:11,020 --> 00:29:12,050
[Zhengnian Hall]

608
00:29:14,240 --> 00:29:15,350
tanga ka.

609
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:17,620
Gumising ka, Ning Fei.

610
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:19,110
Ning Fei!

611
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,710
Ling Xueying!

612
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:22,830
Ama!

613
00:29:23,310 --> 00:29:24,140
Bitawan mo siya.

614
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:24,920
Ang iyong mga kamay…

615
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:25,410
Hayaan mo.

616
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,040
Bitawan mo siya!

617
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,740
anong ginagawa mo

618
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:30,790
ginagamot ko siya.

619
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:33,880
Sino ang nagturo sa iyo na magpagamot ng isang pasyente

620
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,550
habang nakapikit ng ganyan?

621
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,030
Ikaw.

622
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,010
Ako?

623
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:38,760
Pagbigyan mo ako!

624
00:29:39,790 --> 00:29:41,310
Ama, iligtas mo siya.

625
00:29:41,590 --> 00:29:43,230
Mangyaring tulungan siya.

626
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:47,240
Yung kabaong sa may pintuan

627
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,370
ay handa para sa kanya?

628
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,480
Napapanahon.

629
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:51,120
Kakailanganin natin ito sa lalong madaling panahon.

630
00:29:51,590 --> 00:29:52,030
ama,

631
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:52,830
mangyaring iligtas siya.

632
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,200
Nakikiusap ako na iligtas mo siya.

633
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:54,680
Ama.

634
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:55,970
Iligtas siya?

635
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,350
Nasa pintuan na siya ng kamatayan.

636
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,830
Gusto mo bang sirain ko ang walang bahid na record ko?

637
00:29:58,830 --> 00:29:59,560
Sumama ka sa akin.

638
00:29:59,790 --> 00:30:00,310
ama,

639
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:01,570
anong ginagawa mo

640
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:03,590
Mayroon bang anumang pilak sa iyo?

641
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:05,200
Bayaran mo ako sa kutsero.

642
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:05,830
Aking kahon ng gamot

643
00:30:05,830 --> 00:30:07,400
ay hawak pa rin bilang collateral.

644
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,370
Makinig ka sa akin.

645
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,270
Ang kahon ay mas mahalaga kaysa sa kanya.

646
00:30:09,270 --> 00:30:10,300
Bilisan mo, alis na tayo.

647
00:30:11,070 --> 00:30:11,840
ama,

648
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,430
anong ginagawa mo

649
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:17,950
Binayaran mo ako sa kutsero?

650
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:19,860
Salamat, Kamahalan.

651
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:21,080
Panginoon Ling.

652
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:23,400
Nagkaroon na ako ng mga taong
naghahanap sa iyo sa lahat ng dako.

653
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,030
Bakit naging

654
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:25,110
ang hirap mong hanapin?

655
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:27,750
Hiniling sa akin ng isang pasyente
na maghanap ng gamot para sa kanya.

656
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:29,010
Ano ang kailangan mo sa akin?

657
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:30,630
Natural, kailangan ko ng tulong mo.

658
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:33,680
Kailangan kong suriin mo ang pinsala ng isang kaibigan.

659
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,920
Anong klaseng kaibigan

660
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:37,320
karapat-dapat ba ang ganitong pag-aalala
mula sa Kamahalan?

661
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:39,070
Nasa loob siya.

662
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:40,650
Sumama ka sa akin.

663
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:44,240
Ama.

664
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:44,830
Halika.

665
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:49,880
Ikuyom mo ang iyong kamao.

666
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:52,480
Mas mahirap.

667
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:58,730
Sige.

668
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,200
Tingnan ko.

669
00:31:01,930 --> 00:31:03,270
Bukod sa sugat sa iyong kamay,

670
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:04,530
may amnesia ka din.

671
00:31:04,550 --> 00:31:05,980
Nahulog mula sa taas na iyon

672
00:31:06,070 --> 00:31:07,440
at hindi natatapos sa mga piraso,

673
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,790
dapat nahuli ka

674
00:31:08,790 --> 00:31:10,030
sa pamamagitan ng mga sanga sa daan pababa.

675
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,350
Pinabagal nila ang iyong pagkahulog.

676
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:12,680
Kung tungkol sa amnesia,

677
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:14,340
dahil ito ay mula sa isang trauma sa ulo,

678
00:31:14,830 --> 00:31:16,880
ibig sabihin may namuo sa utak mo.

679
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,730
Ang clot

680
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:19,090
ay ang tunay na problema.

681
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,830
Maaaring muling ikabit ang mga punit na litid.

682
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:22,270
Kung tungkol sa namuong dugo,

683
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:23,270
sa oras at paggamot,

684
00:31:23,270 --> 00:31:24,130
maaari itong ayusin.

685
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:25,400
Yixiao,

686
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:26,240
sabi ko sayo

687
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:28,000
tiyak na pagagalingin ka ng aking ama.

688
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,600
salamat po.

689
00:31:29,100 --> 00:31:30,630
Mayroon akong mahirap na kahilingan.

690
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,340
Ang aking pinsala ay hindi

691
00:31:32,430 --> 00:31:34,230
sulit na abalahin ka, Lord Ling.

692
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,270
Sana lang kayanin mo

693
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:36,390
iligtas mo ang kapatid ko.

694
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,310
Kuya?

695
00:31:42,710 --> 00:31:44,300
Yung naghihingalong lalaki sa kama?

696
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:46,130
Oo.

697
00:31:46,350 --> 00:31:47,270
Hindi ka pa ba nakapaghanda

698
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:48,200
isang kabaong para sa kanya?

699
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:50,340
Mas mabuting ilibing na siya kaagad.

700
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:51,480
ama,

701
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:52,750
seryoso ka ba pupunta

702
00:31:52,750 --> 00:31:53,400
para hayaan na lang siyang mamatay?

703
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,350
Seryoso ako.

704
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:56,070
Ang kanyang pulso ay mababaw, mabilis na kumukupas,

705
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:57,750
halos wala na—
mga senyales lang ng heart failure.

706
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:58,350
Hindi na magtatagal

707
00:31:58,350 --> 00:31:59,640
bago siya bumuntong hininga.

708
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,480
Ako, si Ling Feng, ay gumagamot lamang

709
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:01,740
ang mga maaaring maligtas.

710
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:03,490
Hindi ko kailanman ipinaglaban si Hades para sa isang kaluluwa.

711
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:05,520
Panginoon Ling.

712
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,720
Pakiusap, iligtas mo siya!

713
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:08,180
Yixiao, huwag mong gawin ito.

714
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:09,220
ama,

715
00:32:09,220 --> 00:32:10,380
Si Yixiao ay kapatid ko.

716
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,030
Kapatid niya

717
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:11,950
ay ang aking kapatid.

718
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:14,350
Lord Ling, ang iyong kakayahan ay walang kaparis.

719
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:15,640
Dapat may ibang paraan.

720
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:16,590
Kung kaya mo siyang iligtas,

721
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:17,440
Gagawin ko lahat ng hilingin mo.

722
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,030
Miss,

723
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:19,770
ang mga tuntunin ay mga tuntunin.

724
00:32:19,830 --> 00:32:20,880
Walang halaga ng pagsusumamo na magbabago nito.

725
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,660
Bumangon ka na.

726
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,400
hindi ko gagawin.

727
00:32:22,650 --> 00:32:23,270
Panginoon Ling,

728
00:32:23,350 --> 00:32:24,030
ang iyong mga kasanayan

729
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:24,880
maaaring gumawa ng mga himala,

730
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,720
at ikaw ay may mabait na puso.

731
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:26,510
Pakiusap, pakiusap ko.

732
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:27,480
Hindi mo siya pwedeng hayaan na lang mamatay.

733
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:27,830
Yixiao.

734
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:28,400
kaya ko!

735
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:29,520
Lord Ling!

736
00:32:31,750 --> 00:32:32,400
Yixiao.

737
00:32:35,110 --> 00:32:35,680
Ama!

738
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,570
Hintayin mo ako, Ama.

739
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:46,240
Kapatid ko siya.

740
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,270
Dapat tulungan mo siya.

741
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,400
Zhengnian Hall.

742
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,640
Nasa Yujing ako ngayon.

743
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:54,400
Kailangan ko ng matutuluyan, di ba?

744
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:55,840
Bukod,

745
00:32:55,960 --> 00:32:56,830
Zhengnian Villa

746
00:32:56,830 --> 00:32:57,720
pagkakaroon ng sangay sa Yujing

747
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,220
ay hindi isang masamang bagay, tama?

748
00:32:59,370 --> 00:33:00,290
Napakalaking bahay

749
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:01,310
dapat mahal.

750
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:02,840
Saan mo nakuha ang pera?

