761
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:22,120
Gayundin,

762
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,510
ang lalaking iyon ay halos
nasa kanyang libingan na,

763
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:25,010
at gusto mong iligtas ko siya?

764
00:33:25,110 --> 00:33:25,920
Bakit hindi mo na lang ako ilibing

765
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,270
